%h1
	Minecraft HD Skin Server version 1.1

%p
	Find out more about HDSkins by following Mine Little Pony on Github.com. This server provides support for both a Legacy (flat) skin server, as well as a more complex Valhalla minecraft skin server.
	For an explanation of this server and its capabilities see
	%a{href: about_path} here.
	
%div
	%a{href: texture_index_path} Texture search

%br
%b Profiles
%table.full-width
	%tr
		%td Uuid
		%td Username
		%td Created At
		%td Updated At
	- Profile.order(:updated_at).reverse_order.limit(10).each do|profile|
		%tr
			%td= profile.uuid
			%td= profile.username
			%td= profile.created_at
			%td= profile.updated_at

%br
%b Textures
%table.full-width
	%tr
		%td Type
		%td Model
		%td Url
		%td Created At
		%td Updated At
		%td User
	- Texture.active.order(:updated_at).reverse_order.limit(10).each do|texture|
		%tr
			%td= texture.type
			%td= texture.model
			%td
				%a{target: '__blank', href: texture.url}= texture.url
			%td= texture.created_at
			%td= texture.updated_at
			%td= texture.profile.username